### MVP
- 1. Connect to lobby
	- start client, start server
	- connect to a lobby
	- have some interactive button/field to send actions to the other client
		- -> N clients are in a lobby, one presses on the TEST button, the others screen turns red or whatever
- 2. Dominion with simple cards only
	- this includes cards with following abilities
		- treasures -> Behaviour: gainCoins
		- victory -> Behaviour: gainPoints
			- garden -> Behaviour: gardenBehaviour
		- Maybe also: simple actions: -> Behaviour: gainCoins, gainBuys, gainActions
			- no drawCards or complex behaviours
	- implement the game with only trivial cards (no action)
	- everything except actions
- 3. Dominion with action cards, no attacks
	- this includes all cards with complex behaviour that are still "single step" (e.g. no Militia e al.)
- 4. Dominion with all base set cards

